Package com.codename1.rad.ui.table

This package contains bindable implementations of the classes in the ca.weblite.shared.components.table package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntityListTableCellEditor
    A cell editor for editing cell in a Table that uses EntityListTableModel as a model.
    EntityListTableCellRenderer
    A renderer for rendering cells of Tables that use EntityListTableModel as a model.
    EntityListTableModel<T extends Entity>
    A table model that allows using a Table to render and edit an EntityList.
